Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.77,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Marcelo into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.85,EN,,0,0,0,,To see Machiavelli's play?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.68,EN,,0,0,0,,Ezio, his play closed at three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.85,EN,,0,0,0,,I missed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:29.56,EN,,0,0,0,,We're visiting your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on Flavia, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:35.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Sì, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.72,EN,,0,0,0,,We will be back soon. Ciao, amore mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:42.02,EN,,0,0,0,,A più tardi. Be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.89,EN,,0,0,0,,Flavia, tesoro, stay where I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.39,EN,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Lei gentile, papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Go inside, Flavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.43,EN,,0,0,0,,I do not know what else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.06,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I do not want any part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.56,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.97,EN,,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.97,EN,,0,0,0,,How to lead, to rebuilt my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.89,EN,,0,0,0,,No! For me, that's over, finito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Now I think you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Ezio, she has come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.47,EN,,0,0,0,,Shao Yun, did they say that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.18,EN,,0,0,0,,Would you stay for supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Good! We have a spare bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.18,EN,,0,0,0,,You are welcome to stay a few nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.64,EN,,0,0,0,,Are you Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I can not seem to leave my past behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I started to disactive my life so late, Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.04,EN,,0,0,0,,I know I would not have enough time to do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Now I worry that I do not have enough time to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.26,EN,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.42,EN,,0,0,0,,Shao Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.40,EN,,0,0,0,,The wind, it opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.58,EN,,0,0,0,,Fuori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:35.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.66,EN,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Sì. I think you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.86,EN,,0,0,0,,My name is Ezio Auditore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.77,EN,,0,0,0,,When I was a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.94,EN,,0,0,0,,I had liberty, but I did not see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.34,EN,,0,0,0,,I had time, but I did not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:02.93,EN,,0,0,0,,And I had love, but I did not feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:08.38,EN,,0,0,0,,It would be 41 years before I understood the meaning of all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.50,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.31,EN,,0,0,0,,Like you do, to help my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.27,EN,,0,0,0,,I was an assassin for a long time, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:24.31,EN,,0,0,0,,And I know that at any moment, someone could come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Or my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:31.30,EN,,0,0,0,,Do you see? This is why I must to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.47,EN,,0,0,0,,I usually hire people to help me with vintage. The grape harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.68,EN,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:46.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Entra. Let's get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.60,EN,,0,0,0,,I would be lucky if this lasted three seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:17.52,EN,,0,0,0,,This way. I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.56,EN,,0,0,0,,It is nice town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Piena di vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Half of my family was murdered in this piazza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Right there, 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:53.18,EN,,0,0,0,,But now, seeing like this, full of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.27,EN,,0,0,0,,I can not help but feel contain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.90,EN,,0,0,0,,and satisfied that so much pain has faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.27,EN,,0,0,0,,The life of an assassin is pain, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.97,EN,,0,0,0,,You suffer it, you inflict it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.77,EN,,0,0,0,,You watch it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:15.77,EN,,0,0,0,,If there is a hope, but you can't help it disappear in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:22.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Terrible irony, but there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:29.35,EN,,0,0,0,,All right, time to drag this old man back to his villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Yun, Andiamo! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.85,EN,,0,0,0,,It was my mentors wish to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:02.77,EN,,0,0,0,,We left China together, in secret. But these men...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.72,EN,,0,0,0,,They caught him in Venezia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.77,EN,,0,0,0,,Servants of the Emperor Jiajing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:15.27,EN,,0,0,0,,I was born a concubine. My mentor free me when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.85,EN,,0,0,0,,We returned later to save more girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.02,EN,,0,0,0,,but they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.97,EN,,0,0,0,,The Emperor is a cruel man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.64,EN,,0,0,0,,He prefers "Ling Chi" to be heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Ling Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:34.43,EN,,0,0,0,,Slow process... many thousands cuts, then dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.27,EN,,0,0,0,,Pack some bags. You must stay Machiavelli's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.27,EN,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.97,EN,,0,0,0,,A misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Give me just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:32.47,EN,,0,0,0,,When I fought the Borgia, revenge drove me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:37.02,EN,,0,0,0,,And my first impulse was to aim for their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.68,EN,,0,0,0,,In time, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:46.47,EN,,0,0,0,,I learned that those inspire fear have more devoted followers than those who pray each love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:51.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Killing Rodrigo and Cesare will ever accomplish nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.43,EN,,0,0,0,,without some equal measure of brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:13:02.32,EN,,0,0,0,,So, I spent many years to teach men and women think and act for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.98,EN,,0,0,0,,First in Roma, then Costantinopoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.80,EN,,0,0,0,,Love binds our order together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:15.56,EN,,0,0,0,,The love of people, of cultures, of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:20.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Fight to preserve that which in inspires hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.43,EN,,0,0,0,,and you will win back people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:29.86,EN,,0,0,0,,It will take a long time. Long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.20,EN,,0,0,0,,If you do it right, sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.14,EN,,0,0,0,,It's a long way home, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Much to see along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.27,EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.47,EN,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.18,EN,,0,0,0,,This maybe useful one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.18,EN,,0,0,0,,No, only if you lose you way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.47,EN,,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.76,EN,,0,0,0,,We'll be back just after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.35,EN,,0,0,0,,You should have stayed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.97,EN,,0,0,0,,I am home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.77,EN,,0,0,0,,We will be right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Il Diavolo! I hate this damn city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:21.60,EN,,0,0,0,,I wish I was in Roma. I hear the women, there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.35,EN,,0,0,0,,like grape sangiovese wine, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.64,EN,,0,0,0,,Not like here, Firenze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.72,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't think Firenze is your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Prego?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Coraggio vecchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Get some rest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.81,EN,,0,0,0,,When I was a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.81,EN,,0,0,0,,I had liberty, but I did not see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.64,EN,,0,0,0,,I had time, but I did not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.10,EN,,0,0,0,,And I had love, but I did not feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:43.81,EN,,0,0,0,,Many decades would pass before I understood its meaning of all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.31,EN,,0,0,0,,And now, in the twilight of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.43,EN,,0,0,0,,this understanding has passed into contentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:59.68,EN,,0,0,0,,Love, liberty and time, once so disposable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.97,EN,,0,0,0,,are the fuel that drive me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:08.14,EN,,0,0,0,,and love was the especially, mio caro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.27,EN,,0,0,0,,For you, our children,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.77,EN,,0,0,0,,our brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:18.81,EN,,0,0,0,,And for the vast and wonderful world that gave us life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.06,EN,,0,0,0,,and keeps us guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Endless affection, Mia Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.77,EN,,0,0,0,,Forever yours... Ezio Auditore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.56,CN,,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.77,CN,,0,0,0,,我打算帶馬塞羅到城裡去幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.85,CN,,0,0,0,,去看馬基維利的戲劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.68,CN,,0,0,0,,艾吉奧  他的戲劇三個星期前就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.85,CN,,0,0,0,,我已經錯過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:29.56,CN,,0,0,0,,我們要去拜訪一下妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.60,CN,,0,0,0,,你照顧好弗拉維亞  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:35.06,CN,,0,0,0,,放心  我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.72,CN,,0,0,0,,我們很快回來  再見  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:42.02,CN,,0,0,0,,路上注意安全  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.89,CN,,0,0,0,,弗拉維亞  別走太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.39,CN,,0,0,0,,放開我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.56,CN,,0,0,0,,她沒有惡意的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.52,CN,,0,0,0,,進屋去 弗拉維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.43,CN,,0,0,0,,我不知道該說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.06,CN,,0,0,0,,對不起  我不想捲進你們的是非
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.56,CN,,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.97,CN,,0,0,0,,想知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.97,CN,,0,0,0,,如何重新建立我領導的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.89,CN,,0,0,0,,不  對我來說那種生活已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.14,CN,,0,0,0,,我認為你該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.10,CN,,0,0,0,,艾吉奧  她可是大老遠來到這的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.47,CN,,0,0,0,,邵雲  是這樣稱呼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.18,CN,,0,0,0,,要不要留下來吃晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.02,CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.60,CN,,0,0,0,,太好了  我們正好有空出的臥室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.18,CN,,0,0,0,,你可以留宿幾晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.64,CN,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我好像還是沒有甩掉過去的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我到了這把年紀才開始過上安定的日子  索菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.04,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道自己沒有足夠的時間去完成一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.28,CN,,0,0,0,,而現在  我恐怕已經什麼都做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.26,CN,,0,0,0,,雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.42,CN,,0,0,0,,邵雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.94,CN,,0,0,0,,你給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.40,CN,,0,0,0,,是風把門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.58,CN,,0,0,0,,快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:35.74,CN,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.66,CN,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.22,CN,,0,0,0,,是的  我覺得你該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.86,CN,,0,0,0,,我的名字叫艾吉奧·奧迪托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.77,CN,,0,0,0,,在我年輕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.94,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有自由  卻未曾看清其珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.34,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有時間 卻茫然不知其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:02.93,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有愛情 卻從未感受其溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:08.38,CN,,0,0,0,,四十一載光陰流逝  我才領悟這三者的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.50,CN,,0,0,0,,我想要弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.31,CN,,0,0,0,,然後就像你那樣  去幫助我的百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.27,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾經做了很長一段時間的刺客  雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:24.31,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道  隨時都可能有人來找我尋仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.08,CN,,0,0,0,,或是報復我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:31.30,CN,,0,0,0,,你明白嗎  所以我必須小心謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.47,CN,,0,0,0,,通常我會僱人在豐收季節來幫忙摘葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.68,CN,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:46.06,CN,,0,0,0,,不說這些了  我們去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.60,CN,,0,0,0,,如果這能維持三個季節就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:17.52,CN,,0,0,0,,這邊走  我給你看些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.56,CN,,0,0,0,,這裡不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.10,CN,,0,0,0,,充滿活力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.14,CN,,0,0,0,,我半個家族的人在這個廣場被處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.72,CN,,0,0,0,,就在四十五年前的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:53.18,CN,,0,0,0,,但現在  你看看  一片繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.27,CN,,0,0,0,,我已經感到滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.90,CN,,0,0,0,,也漸漸淡忘了痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.27,CN,,0,0,0,,刺客的一生是痛苦的  雲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.97,CN,,0,0,0,,你要受苦  抑或使別人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.77,CN,,0,0,0,,只能眼睜睜看著痛苦降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:15.77,CN,,0,0,0,,但你卻沒辦法從這痛苦中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:22.22,CN,,0,0,0,,很諷刺吧  但事實就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:29.35,CN,,0,0,0,,好了  該把我這個老頭送回莊園了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.60,CN,,0,0,0,,雲  快離開這  快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.85,CN,,0,0,0,,本來是我師父要來找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:02.77,CN,,0,0,0,,我們偷偷離開中原  但是這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.72,CN,,0,0,0,,他們在威尼斯抓住了我師父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.14,CN,,0,0,0,,他們都是些什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.77,CN,,0,0,0,,都是嘉靖皇帝的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:15.27,CN,,0,0,0,,我是妾室出身  是師父在我小時候把我救了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.85,CN,,0,0,0,,後來我們想要回去解救更多的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.02,CN,,0,0,0,,但她們都被…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.97,CN,,0,0,0,,那狗皇帝心腸歹毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.64,CN,,0,0,0,,比起斬首  他更喜歡用凌遲處死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.56,CN,,0,0,0,,凌遲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:34.43,CN,,0,0,0,,將身上的肉一片一片慢慢割下來  直到死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.27,CN,,0,0,0,,趕緊收拾下  今晚你到馬基維利家去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.27,CN,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.97,CN,,0,0,0,,一個誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我這就去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:32.47,CN,,0,0,0,,在我對抗波奇亞家族的時候  復仇就是我的動力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:37.02,CN,,0,0,0,,我第一反應就是砍掉他們的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.68,CN,,0,0,0,,但後來我發現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:46.47,CN,,0,0,0,,他們那些散播恐懼的人比我們這些宣揚真善美的人擁有更多的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:51.02,CN,,0,0,0,,所以只幹掉羅德里戈和凱撒是遠遠不夠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.43,CN,,0,0,0,,必須要建立一個與他們實力相當的兄弟會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:13:02.32,CN,,0,0,0,,因此我花了很多年的時間教導人們  如何有自己的思想與作為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.98,CN,,0,0,0,,先是在羅馬  然後是君士坦丁堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.80,CN,,0,0,0,,是愛  讓我們緊緊地團結在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:15.56,CN,,0,0,0,,是那些人與人  人與文化  人與世界的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:20.08,CN,,0,0,0,,為了我們的信仰而去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.43,CN,,0,0,0,,這樣才能贏得人心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:29.86,CN,,0,0,0,,那需要很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.20,CN,,0,0,0,,如果你的做法正確  那便是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.14,CN,,0,0,0,,休息去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.14,CN,,0,0,0,,回家的路很長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.56,CN,,0,0,0,,這一路上我一定能學到很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.27,CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝您  導師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.47,CN,,0,0,0,,拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.18,CN,,0,0,0,,說不定哪天會用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.18,CN,,0,0,0,,不  等你迷失方向時再打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.47,CN,,0,0,0,,一路保重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.76,CN,,0,0,0,,我們會在天黑之前回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.35,CN,,0,0,0,,你應該待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.97,CN,,0,0,0,,這就是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.77,CN,,0,0,0,,我們去逛逛就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.22,CN,,0,0,0,,該死的  我恨這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:21.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我真希望現在是在羅馬  聽說那裡的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.35,CN,,0,0,0,,就像美酒一樣  你懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.64,CN,,0,0,0,,不像這裡  佛羅倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.72,CN,,0,0,0,,我覺得你的問題不在於佛羅倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.72,CN,,0,0,0,,你剛說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.28,CN,,0,0,0,,真是一名勇敢的老人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.06,CN,,0,0,0,,好好歇著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.81,CN,,0,0,0,,在我年輕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有自由  卻未曾看清其珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.64,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有時間  卻茫然不知其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.10,CN,,0,0,0,,我曾擁有愛情  卻從未感受其溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:43.81,CN,,0,0,0,,數十載光陰流逝  我才領悟這三者的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.31,CN,,0,0,0,,如今  垂暮之年的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.43,CN,,0,0,0,,將這些領悟視為一筆財富
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:59.68,CN,,0,0,0,,愛情  自由  時間  是它們教會了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.97,CN,,0,0,0,,如何指引自己前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:08.14,CN,,0,0,0,,而愛情尤為特別  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.27,CN,,0,0,0,,無論是你  還是我們的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.77,CN,,0,0,0,,或是我們的兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:18.81,CN,,0,0,0,,還有這個賜予我們生命的廣袤世間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.06,CN,,0,0,0,,是如此令人捉摸不透
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.52,CN,,0,0,0,,致我摯愛的妻子  索菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.77,CN,,0,0,0,,永遠愛你的  艾吉奧·奧迪托雷
